Pre-Game Insights: Pakistan have had the better of South Africa with three wins in previous four meetings, but they will need to improve their performance by a lot, to challenge them on October 27.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Pakistan's batters have struggled to score runs at a quick rate, with the top order of Abdullah Shafique, Imam-ul-Haq, and Babar Azam, finding themselves under more pressure.
South Africa batters have managed to score totals in excess of 300 runs in four out of five occasions during the ODI World Cup 2023.
Others: The match will be played at the MA Chidambaram Stadium in Chennai on October 27, 2023.
The Protea bowlers have shared wickets amongst themselves regularly in the flagship tournament, while being spearheaded by the experienced Kagiso Rabada and Keshav Maharaj.
